Play with linked lists and binary trees easily !

This library provides a basic set of functions for both structures.

Only one rule to use the library, declare your structures like this :

  ----------------------------------------------------
  |      Linked lists      |      Binary trees       |
  |------------------------|--------------------------
  |  struct list {         |  struct tree {          |
  |    struct list *next;  |    struct tree *left;   |
  |    ...                 |    struct tree *right;  |
  |  };                    |    ...                  |
  |                        |  };                     |
  ----------------------------------------------------
